Create a program to for a store to keep track of its data - the customers, purchases and balance.
Allow user to:

1.	Add a new Customer 
2. Remove a Customer 
3.	Add a customer purchase(for a particular customer , a particular item) 
4.	Return a Customer purchase  (for a particular customer, a particular PurchasedItem)
5.	View Customer purchases (of a particular Customer) 
6.	List the Names of Customers who have purchased a particular Item name
7.	For each Customer, list how many times the Customer has purchased a particular item 
8.	List which customers have purchased at least one item of a given item type 
0. exit

